trials.strategy: To clear regions, I started from the middle and worked outwards to see if the grid was simple, if the outsides were empty I would just move onto the next
trials.gridmostopened: The star-grids with complex patterns that took the entire region
trials.gridsleastopened: The type of star-grids that only had a pattern in the middle and nothing else along the sides.
trials.moveon: When I figured out the patter of the star-grid or was satisfied with what I've seen
